                <h1>Discover the Rich History of the Grammy Awards</h1>
                <p>The Grammy Awards, established in 1959, celebrate musical excellence across genres. Presented by the Recording Academy, these prestigious awards recognize outstanding artists and their contributions to the music industry. The iconic golden gramophone trophy symbolizes artistic achievement and is highly coveted among musicians worldwide.</p>
